OL,3,C'Public health crisis' declared after
OL,4,C'shocking' HMO conditions
OL,6,FSalford council have now vowed to
OL,7,Flaunch a "crackdown on rogue
OL,8,Flandlords" in the city who are renting
OL,9,Fout homes with major safety hazards.
OL,11,FSalford Mayor Dennett and his cabinet
OL,12,Fteam at the council agreed to launch a
OL,13,Fconsultation on plans for a city-wide
OL,14,Fadditional licensing scheme for
OL,15,FSection 257 HMOs.
OL,17,FThe City Mayor said Salford 'is the
OL,18,Ffirst local authority in Greater
OL,19,FManchester' to be taking such a step
OL,20,Fto drive up housing standards.
