OL,3,C'Public health crisis' declared after
OL,4,C'shocking' HMO conditions
OL,6,FThe scheme would require landlords to
OL,7,Fbe licensed by the council, giving the
OL,8,Ftown hall better insight into the
OL,9,Fconditions tenants are living in.
OL,11,FHMOs not up to the required standards
OL,12,Fcould then face enforcement measures
OL,13,Fincluding fines or prosecution,
OL,14,Faccording to a council report.
OL,16,FThe report explained that if the
OL,17,Flicensing scheme is introduced, around
OL,18,F425 properties would have to receive
OL,19,Frenovations across the city.
