OL,3,C'Public health crisis' declared after
OL,4,C'shocking' HMO conditions
OL,6,FMr Dennett said: "Landlords should be
OL,7,Fashamed of themselves operating these
OL,8,Fsorts of properties in the city of
OL,9,FSalford.
OL,11,F"Today we are saying yes we are going
OL,12,Fout to consultation, but I want today
OL,13,Fto be a very firm message to HMO
OL,14,Flandlords that they really do need to
OL,15,Fget their act together because the
OL,16,Fpeople of Salford deserve better, I am
OL,17,Fdeeply concerned about this.
