OL,3,C'Public health crisis' declared after
OL,4,C'shocking' HMO conditions
OL,6,FThe move comes after Salford council
OL,7,Fsaid last summer that it had handed
OL,8,Fout #2.2 million in fines to landlords
OL,9,Frenting out unsafe properties.
OL,11,FIn July, the council said 26 landlords
OL,12,Fof HMOs in Salford were hit with fines
OL,13,Fof more than #500,000.
OL,15,FIncome from penalties has been re-
OL,16,Finvested into the council's housing
OL,17,Fstandards and enforcement team to go
OL,18,Fout and inspect more properties.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
