OL,4,C'shocking' HMO conditions
OL,6,FMr Dennett said Salford's landlords
OL,7,Fwould 'welcome' an additional HMO
OL,8,Flicensing scheme in the city because
OL,9,Fit would help to keep tenants safe.
OL,11,FHe added: "The sooner we act the
OL,12,Fbetter because goodness knows what's
OL,13,Fgoing on in the ones we have not
OL,14,Finspected."
